<topic id="preferences-editor-annotations">
    <title>Annotations Preferences</title>
    <body>
        <p>To open the <uicontrol>Annotations</uicontrol> preferences page go to <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>General</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Editors</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Text Editors</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Annotations</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>.</p>
        <p>The following <ph keyref="product"/>
            preferences are available:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><uicontrol>XSLT/XQuery Debug Current Instruction Pointer</uicontrol> - Controls the
                background color of the current execution node, both in the document (XML) and
                XSL/XQuery views.</li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</topic>
